## Project: ARAPropertyServiceApp

**Stack:** SwiftUI + SwiftData + WorkOS Auth + Convex Backend
**Architecture:** MVVM (Models, ViewModels, Views, Services, Utilities)
**Models:** Issue, Contact, FieldTask, ChatMessage, Facility, CleaningAlert, AppNotification, UserAccount, Organization, OrganizationMembership
**Services:** WorkOS Auth, Convex, Keychain, Biometric Auth, Barcode Scanner, Apple Sign-In, Document Picker, Print
**Theme:** Dark mode (ARATheme), custom tab bar (9 tabs)

